def auto_off '{
  """
  Turn off any automatic filter and exposure adjustments.

  USAGE::

    > auto_off

  NOTE:
    This command is equivalent to ``auto_set_level 0``

  SEE ALSO:
    :spec:def:`auto_set_level`,
    :spec:def:`auto_on`

  """

